name: ralts

diamond: Sinnoh Route 204 South Towards Jubilife City
pearl: Sinnoh Route 204 South Towards Jubilife City
platinum: Sinnoh Route 212 North Towards Hearthome City

flavorText:
RALTS senses the emotions of
people using the horns on its head.
This POKMON rarely appears before people. But when it does, it draws
closer if it senses that the person has
a positive disposition.
